snippet.title: Spiders in Amber, Fossils, and Crystals, OH MY! Unboxing Incredible Treasures Sent in Over the Year!
snippet.description:
In this one, we unbox a bunch of amazing treasures sent in from other channels and a viewer! Included are some incredible fossil specimens from Michael Van Dyke, breath taking crystal specimens from Du5tin Finds Rocks, a fantastic pile of Michigan Septarians, and even some insect filled amber specimens from Amberscape! We hand pick a few specimens to polish and my gosh are the results amazing! Look forward to seeing more of this material very soon! Those turritella agates and septarians are begging to get cut! I hope you all enjoy this one and I will have another one out very soon!


Make sure to subscribe to the amazing and generous channels that sent us these treasures!

@Michael VanDyke : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCdOBYmWrGf5tHsQelLdAakw

@Dustin Finds Rocks  : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqBqvPtxF8JV9tgufvN47Ww
